com.revolsys.io.filter

Class ExtensionFilenameFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.revolsys.io.filter.ExtensionFilenameFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileFilter, FilenameFilter

    public class ExtensionFilenameFilter
extends Object
implements FilenameFilter, FileFilter
    The ExtensionFilenameFilter is a FilenameFilter that only returns files if the have one of the specified file extensions. More than one file extension can be specified by using the addExtension(String) method.
    Author:
    Paul Austin
